<ul>
<li>no bars in bar graph
<li>no tick marks on bar graph
<li>pH slider scale doesn't line up with bar graph
<li>linear and log scale options for bar graph don't work
<li>no zoom buttons for linear graph
</ul>
<p>
<b>Know issues:</b>
